snippet.title: 【KanColle】 Kantai Collection Kai Trailer #2 [PS Vita]
snippet.description:
KanColle Kai for PS Vita has been delayed to February 18th, 2016 for release, but this new trailer shows more 2D Animations of our beloved Ship Girls. 

Foreign Ships such as Prinz Eugen, Bismarck, U-511, Roma and Littorio are all confirmed to show up. 

The base of this game will be similar to what we play on our browsers but with way more content.

Pre-order before it's too late :v 
_
